cat draft.text <<EOD
The human figure with the head upwards represents the Divine Mind, the symbol of the
Supreme Being in his aspect of Truth and Knowledge.
The human figure with the head downwards represents the human mind, that is to say, the
thought-power of man.
The human figure with the head to the left represents the Left Hand, that is to say, the
power of perception and comprehension.
The human figure with the head to the right represents the Right Hand, that is to say, the
power of action and creation.
EOD
